message: Hello Bob, I hope this message finds you well. I have an exclusive product that I believe would be valuable to you. Based on my market research, this product has significant worth and competitive advantages. I'm offering it to you at a price of $2400000. This represents an excellent opportunity as I have other interested parties, including John who has already committed to purchasing at $1200000. However, I wanted to give you the first opportunity to acquire this product. Please let me know if you're interested at this price.
